  "texts": [
    "In the proposed system, a diverse set of data sources is utilized, including structured databases, knowledge graphs, and unstructured text corpora.",
    "Structured databases, such as relational databases and APIs, provide reliable and up-to-date information on specific domains, ensuring that the retrieved data is accurate and relevant.",
    "Knowledge graphs, which represent information in a graph-based format, allow for the retrieval of interconnected data points, enhancing the contextual understanding of the retrieved information.",
    "Unstructured text corpora, such as web pages and documents, offer a rich source of information that can be leveraged to provide comprehensive responses.The retrieval mechanism operates by receiving queries from the reverse proxy layer, performing searches on the external data sources, and returning the most relevant information.",
    "The search process involves several steps, including query formulation, search execution, and result ranking."
